no-restricted-syntax.message:
❌ Hardcoded color classes detected! Use design tokens instead:

  ✅ GOOD:
    import { color } from '@/lib/design-tokens';
    className={color('primary', 600, 'bg')}

  ✅ OR use pre-composed tokens:
    import { tokens } from '@/lib/design-tokens';
    className={tokens.button.primary}

  ❌ BAD:
    className="bg-blue-600"

❌ Hardcoded spacing classes detected! Use design tokens instead:

  ✅ GOOD:
    import { spacing } from '@/lib/design-tokens';
    className={spacing(4, 'p')}
    className={spacing(6, 'm', 'x')}

  ❌ BAD:
    className="p-4 mx-6"
